  "detailed_description": "Get ready to dive into the high-speed, action-packed world of <strong>Skyline Savior</strong>!<br><br>Take control of Sam’s car and navigate through a series of exciting and challenging environments. With a unique set of abilities at your disposal, you’ll need to overcome difficult obstacles to become the ultimate hero of the skies.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Thrilling Gameplay Mechanics</u></h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Arcadey Car Movement</strong>: Enjoy smooth, responsive driving with the ability to jump, dash, and perform awesome stunts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Magnet</strong>: Use the car’s magnet to interact with various magnets around the map, overcoming obstacles by attracting or repelling the car.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Slow Motion</strong>: Slow down time to navigate through tricky sequences and nail those precise maneuvers. You are falling down? Slow the time down so you can afford waiting for the dash cooldown to end.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Dash and Downforce</strong>: Get a burst of speed with the dash ability to cover distances quickly. Activate the Downforce skill to push the car down, like a reverse jump, allowing for precise landings and new strategic moves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Game Modes</u></h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Regular Mode</strong>: Navigate through levels with strategically placed checkpoints, allowing you to respawn and continue from key points.<br></li><li><strong>Pretty Hard Mode</strong>: Embrace the ultimate challenge with no checkpoints from start to finish, pushing your skills and endurance to the limit.<br></li><li><strong>Impossible Mode</strong>: On top of not having checkpoints, you also don’t have dash and boost skills! Need more challenge? The magnet is now limited to a specific number of seconds. Good luck!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Get ready to dive into the high-speed, action-packed world of <strong>Skyline Savior</strong>!<br><br>Take control of Sam’s car and navigate through a series of exciting and challenging environments. With a unique set of abilities at your disposal, you’ll need to overcome difficult obstacles to become the ultimate hero of the skies.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Thrilling Gameplay Mechanics</u></h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Arcadey Car Movement</strong>: Enjoy smooth, responsive driving with the ability to jump, dash, and perform awesome stunts.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/d168ee9e92133daf8c5087317ccaf288.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Magnet</strong>: Use the car’s magnet to interact with various magnets around the map, overcoming obstacles by attracting or repelling the car.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/704e184774d3b2069f3e38f31a3db3fb.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Slow Motion</strong>: Slow down time to navigate through tricky sequences and nail those precise maneuvers. You are falling down? Slow the time down so you can afford waiting for the dash cooldown to end.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/98491e145a625d119898ee6d781fbaa9.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Dash and Downforce</strong>: Get a burst of speed with the dash ability to cover distances quickly. Activate the Downforce skill to push the car down, like a reverse jump, allowing for precise landings and new strategic moves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.poster.avif?t=1746032406\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.webm?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122710/extras/8f1c27fd3ed48aee86446896562d0dea.mp4?t=1746032406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>Game Modes</u></h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Regular Mode</strong>: Navigate through levels with strategically placed checkpoints, allowing you to respawn and continue from key points.<br></li><li><strong>Pretty Hard Mode</strong>: Embrace the ultimate challenge with no checkpoints from start to finish, pushing your skills and endurance to the limit.<br></li><li><strong>Impossible Mode</strong>: On top of not having checkpoints, you also don’t have dash and boost skills! Need more challenge? The magnet is now limited to a specific number of seconds. Good luck!</li></ul>",
